Project: mcMMO‑SP (Single‑Player Port)
Based on: mcMMO by the mcMMO team (https://github.com/mcMMO-Dev/mcMMO)
Original license: GNU General Public License v3.0 (GPL‑3.0). See LICENSE file. 

What this fork is
This repository contains a single‑player port and related changes to adapt mcMMO for local/single‑player use.
All original code from mcMMO remains under GPL‑3.0. This fork’s modifications are also released under GPL‑3.0.

How to obtain source
The full source for every distributed binary is available in this repository and in the Releases section. Binary downloads include a link to this source and the LICENSE file. 

Attribution and credits
This project is a fork of mcMMO (https://github.com/mcMMO-Dev/mcMMO). Original authors and contributors retain copyright; see CONTRIBUTORS.md for details. 
